{"id":147207,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/报告称政府对公民的网络攻击在加剧/","date":"2011-04-24T19:50:42Z","modified":"2011-04-24T19:50:42Z","title":"报告称政府对公民的网络攻击在加剧","content":"<p>自由之家公布了2011年度互联网自由报告(PDF)，报告称国家对自己公民的网络攻击在加剧，认为约旦、俄罗斯、泰国、委内瑞拉、津巴布韦、中国、伊朗、突尼斯和白俄罗斯这12个国家在未来12个月内的网络镇压会恶化。报告认为中国是全球网络攻击的主要源头。根据互联网自由排名，排在中国之后的是古巴、缅甸和伊朗。伊朗政府控制的伊朗网军攻击了大量网站。<img src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1457e313/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%A7%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E5%9C%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%89%A7&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F21%2F0854238%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%A7%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E5%9C%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%89%A7&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F21%2F0854238%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100752255510/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1457e313/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100752255510/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1457e313/a2.img\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=70_YDvqWtiE:o5aC89ojuz8:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=70_YDvqWtiE:o5aC89ojuz8:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/soli